    "content": "<!-- AI-IMAGE: success-hero-bg | Form success confirmation hero. Reassuring, bright, positive.\n       SEARCH KEYWORDS: smiling patient, dental confirmation, welcoming office scene, bright reception.\n       REQUIREMENTS: Landscape, minimum 1920x800, professional quality.\n       FALLBACK: Any bright welcoming dental photo.\n       INSTRUCTION: Replace ONLY the url() value inside the section's background-image style; keep the linear-gradient overlay intact. Do not render this as an <img> element. -->\n<section class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-success-hero relative w-full min-h-[560px] md:min-h-[680px] flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden py-20 md:py-24 bg-center bg-cover bg-no-repeat text-ivory\" style=\"background-image:linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(15,23,42,0.75), rgba(15,23,42,0.55), rgba(15,23,42,0.85)), url('https://picsum.photos/1920/1080?random=100');\">\n  <div class=\"max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center\">\n\n    <div class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-success-hero-component-icon w-24 h-24 md:w-28 md:h-28 mx-auto mb-10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center bg-primary\">\n      <svg class=\"w-12 h-12 md:w-14 md:h-14 text-white\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\">\n        <path d=\"M5 13l4 4L19 7\"></path>\n      </svg>\n    </div>\n\n    <h1 class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-success-hero-component-heading font-serif text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-medium leading-tight mb-6\">\n      You're All Set!\n    </h1>\n\n    <p class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-success-hero-component-subtext text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed mb-4 max-w-2xl mx-auto\">\n      Thank you for reaching out to our practice. Our team will review your submission and contact you within one business day to confirm your appointment and answer any questions you may have.\n    </p>\n\n    <p class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-success-hero-component-body text-base leading-relaxed mb-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto\">\n      In the meantime, feel free to browse our website to learn more about our services, meet our team, or find directions to our office. We look forward to seeing you soon.\n    </p>\n\n    <a href=\"/\" class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-success-hero-component-cta inline-block text-base md:text-lg py-4 px-10 rounded-full font-medium transition-opacity duration-200 hover:opacity-90 text-white no-underline font-sans bg-primary\">\n      Back to Homepage\n    </a>\n\n  </div>\n</section>"
